## Challenge Name: CodeBook
## Level Easy
## Description: Run the Python Script code.py in the same directory as codebook.txt


## Steps taken:
1. Log into the PicoCTF webshell
2. wget https://artifacts.picoctf.net/c/2/code.py
3. wget https://artifacts.picoctf.net/c/2/codebook.txt
4. Made sure code.py and codebook.txt were in the same directory by typing "ls"
5. executed code.py by running python3 code.py
6. Obtained and submitted the flag. 


